{"tid":1562301,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽]真相好重要但對於運動黎講唔係最重要","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T03:13:41.000Z","uid":305022,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9eafe1fff80c86320eeed76be907c3d5b46a89","tid":1562301,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"811,831搵事實真相當然係非常重要，但對於我地黎講，不如問番自己，如果真係有死人，有強姦，咁點？<br />\n.<br />\n如果你既答案係嬲囉，呢一世都唔會原諒黑警囉，但係無咩實際升級行動，咁得罪講句，有乜撚用？<br />\n.<br />\n升級行動唔一定係指一啲好激進好高風險既行為，有時可能係每日做運動以備不時之需，或者係用盡一切方法將20%既收入投入抗爭活動都可以係一種升級，見仁見智，量力而為，但唔好得個嬲字．<br />\n.<br />\n懇請各位真係問自己以上既問題，一定要好切身處地咁去問，甚至乎要諗埋點樣實行你個計劃。做一個對得住自己對得住手足既人，計劃得出就做得到，當自己立下左重誓。我已經有個計劃，如果中秋之前無任何有証據既說法証明無死人，我自己會升級，你地呢？"},{"pid":"3f058f3917c00fc228f3cb6a1f067c41a449bfe5","tid":1562301,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b25722321e873c7d35246d2e19651417c383a5d1","tid":1562301,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a><br />\